first run npm init to install package.json on server side
then run this command to install some packages
        npm i express cors dotenv nodemon jsonwebtoken mongoose bcryptjs nodemailer cookie-parser
express- to create backend
cors- to connect front end 
dotenv- to store environment variable in backend
nodemon- help to restart backend
jsonwedtoken- token for authentication
moongose- help to connect with mongodb
bcryptjs- encrypte the password and store in database
nodemailer- help us to send email
cookie-parser- help to send cookie in api response.

//for client side 
run npm create vite@latest 
npm install
npm insatll axios react-router-dom react-toastify

1- axios means to connect with apis
2- react-tostify means notification on web 

install vite+taiwind css